  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.6">
<l>tōyā viṉtayir neyyamu tuṇṇac coṉṉār collina kumparicē peṟṟa</l>
<l>tāyā lāppuṇṭi runtaḻu tēṅkun tāṭā ḷātarai yōrkkumviṇ ṇōrkkum</l>
<l>cēyāy kirētati rētatu vāpa rakali yukamivai nāṉkumu ṉāṉāy</l>
<l>āyā niṉṉaṭi yaṉṟimaṟ ṟaṟiyē ṉaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of powerful feet who sobbed, wailing,</l>
<l rend="indent">being tied by the mother who got [you],</l>
<l>When you ate the sweet, uncongealed curds, ghee, and milk</l>
<l rend="indent">in a way that those who spoke, telling [of it], laughed,</l>
<l>You who are remote from those of heaven and those of earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">you who long ago became the four yugas: Kreta, Treta, Dvāpara, and Kali,</l>
<l>Herder, besides your feet, I do not know any[thing] other,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
